## Islamic Content Disclaimer

The Islamic content in this software is provided for educational purposes. While every effort has been made to ensure accuracy and authenticity of Islamic teachings, users are encouraged to:

1. Verify religious content with qualified Islamic scholars
2. Consult authentic Islamic sources (Quran, authentic Hadith collections)
3. Seek guidance from local Islamic authorities for specific religious questions

The developers make no warranties regarding the completeness or accuracy of religious content and are not responsible for any religious guidance or decisions made based on this software.

May Allah (SWT) guide us all to the straight path and forgive any errors in conveying His message.

Barakallahu feekum (May Allah bless you).
